==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to suggest''' (suggesting, suggested)

# To imply but stop short of saying explicitly.
#: ''Are you suggesting that I killed my wife?''
# To ask for without demanding.
#: ''I'd like to suggest that we go out to lunch.''

